Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.92,0:01:16.36,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在那坡道的中途 你先離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.50,0:01:21.93,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}留下了無數珍貴的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.06,0:01:27.21,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我孤單地在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.35,0:01:34.51,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}回味著那些溫馨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:42.61,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只有你 只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.71,0:01:48.58,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只喜歡著你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.70,0:01:56.48,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}風沙遮眼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.60,0:02:03.50,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你漸漸遠去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.39,0:02:05.91,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,600)\pos(320,348)}無論何時 都還記得
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.51,0:02:07.93,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,600)\pos(320,348)}即便一切 天翻地覆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.53,0:02:09.99,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,600)\pos(320,348)}唯有那件 唯有那件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.59,0:02:12.68,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,600)\pos(320,348)}日常之事 不曾改變
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.28,0:02:16.89,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,600)\pos(320,348)}看一看吧 那充滿光芒的唯一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.39,0:02:21.70,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,600)\pos(320,348)}永遠永遠都在守護著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.71,0:22:25.93,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}凝望著朵朵流逝的雲彩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.23,0:22:32.86,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}感受著變化無窮的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.74,0:22:41.07,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}駐足而立的我們察覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.30,0:22:48.26,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}這不斷變遷的世界編織出的歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.35,0:22:55.53,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}彷彿伸出手來追尋一般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.64,0:23:03.99,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}去尋找那恆久不變的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.48,0:23:11.69,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}手裏高舉著的火炬
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.84,0:23:19.50,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}是通向明天的小小路標
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.50,0:23:26.74,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}現在依然明亮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.02,0:23:34.37,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}那一天的言語化為誓約
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.48,0:23:39.22,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}激勵我們前進
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.25,0:03:14.88,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(320,245)}突發事件
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.70,0:24:09.67,notice,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)\an5\pos(320,245)}畢  業
